title: No winning ticket for Lotto Max jackpot, 4 Maxmillions won
text:
Tweet 
Lotto Max players will have to wait at least another week to see if their dreams of striking it rich come true. No winning ticket was sold for Friday night’s $60 million dollar jackpot. The winning numbers in Friday’s Lotto Max draw for an estimated $60 million: 8, 19, 24, 28, 34, 42 & 48. The bonus number was 17. The numbers for encore were 5164494. There were 13 Maxmillion prizes of $1 million each up for grabs, and four of them were claimed by ticket holders in Ontario, Quebec and the Prairies. Story continues below One of those prizes will be shared by two ticket holders. The jackpot for the next Lotto Max draw on Feb. 10 will remain at approximately $60 million, but the number of Maxmillion prizes offered will grow to 26. 01 09 21 22 29 40 4502 03 13 28 32 34 4302 07 16 20 25 27 3202 10 14 20 33 40 4802 11 13 20 28 38 4305 08 11 16 26 42 4305 11 22 27 28 31 3305 12 18 21 36 40 4308 12 14 30 33 41 4808 18 20 23 27 30 4512 21 22 26 30 45 4914 15 16 18 23 24 3914 18 19 22 30 39 43 In the event of any discrepancy between this list and the official winning numbers, the latter shall prevail. none
